<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>HDI Predictor — Human Development Index Estimator</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,600&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='style.css') }}">
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
  <header class="hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">Socio-Economic Indicator Model</span>
    <h1>Human Development<br>Index Predictor</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Enter four core socio-economic indicators — the same ones the United Nations uses to
      compute HDI — and get an instant, model-based estimate of the development score and tier.
    </p>
  </header>

  <main class="panel">
    {% if error %}
    <div class="error-banner">{{ error }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    <form action="/predict" method="POST" class="form-grid">
      <div class="field">
        <label for="life_expectancy">Life expectancy at birth <span>years</span></label>
        <input type="number" step="0.1" min="20" max="90" id="life_expectancy"
               name="life_expectancy" placeholder="e.g. 72.5" required>
        <p class="hint">Health dimension — average years a newborn is expected to live.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="mean_years_schooling">Mean years of schooling <span>years</span></label>
        <input type="number" step="0.1" min="0" max="20" id="mean_years_schooling"
               name="mean_years_schooling" placeholder="e.g. 8.2" required>
        <p class="hint">Education dimension — average schooling completed by adults 25+.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="expected_years_schooling">Expected years of schooling <span>years</span></label>
        <input type="number" step="0.1" min="0" max="22" id="expected_years_schooling"
               name="expected_years_schooling" placeholder="e.g. 13.0" required>
        <p class="hint">Education dimension — schooling a child entering school can expect.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="gni_per_capita">GNI per capita <span>PPP US$</span></label>
        <input type="number" step="1" min="100" max="150000" id="gni_per_capita"
               name="gni_per_capita" placeholder="e.g. 12500" required>
        <p class="hint">Income dimension — gross national income per person.</p>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Predict HDI Score →</button>
    </form>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <span>Gradient Boosting regression &middot; trained on socio-economic indicator data</span>
  </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
